  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you gain access to this founding mystery, you learn to send and receive telepathic messages from a creature who can understand you within 60 feet. By spending 1 Enchantment Point, you can establish a telepathic bond lasting 1 hour, with a creature capable of understanding you within 60 feet, with whom you can share thoughts, feelings and, using an action, vision too. You can cast spells on the creature with whom you are connected telepathically as if it were always within range.</span> </p>",
